 other factors taps early mover advantages access to finite insurer capital operational capacity and current pricing   you may be closer than you think funded status is chief among the many factors to consider when determining how and when to derisk in a rising interest rate environment a plans funded status can be volatile and windows of opportunity to act can be fleeting during the first six months of  us corporate db plan funded status increased from  percent to  percent over the course of  us corporate defined benefit plan funded status increased from  percent to  percent milliman  monthly pension funding index your pension’s funded status may be closer to  percent than you think risking the possibility of trapped assets once you cross the  percent funded status threshold companies with modest underfunding of or adequately funded material pension liabilities are therefore in the prime window of opportunity to focus on derisking and creating additional financial flexibility shifting pension risk to a qualified annuity provider may be more viable than ever the scenario below illustrates the combination of discount rates and equity returns—and the resulting funded status   next our solutions learn more about prudential pension risk transfer our track record our financial strength our commitment a volatile market why derisk current page our solutions list of events done about clal group חברת ביטוח כלל ביטוח  תפריט נגישות עבור לתוכן העמוד צור קשר מפת אתר תאריך הדפסה   תפריט ראשי about  about clal group our vision senior managment board of directors and committees members investors relations  rating financial statements companys presentation canaf  investment division subsidiaries  areas of expertise subsidiaries hewbrew site  קשרי משקיעים דף הבית login userid password investors relations homepage investors relations aגודל גופן מוגדל   aגודל גופן בינוני   aגודל גופן רגיל investors relations about clal group about clal insurance our vision subsidiaries senior managment